comments: Some people might not realize but this is not just a workout, it is also helping to get the right mindset for doing endurance sport. You can't push your heartrate to the limit for 60min if your mind doesn't embrace to get over your own limits.

Finally got cleared after my C-section 8 weeks ago and I'm so excited to be back doing your classes💗 you're amazing, thank you for doing this and sharing these amazing workouts on YouTube for us at home💗💗
I play this various times every week. I don’t do the movements but just the music and the motivation makes this enjoyable every time I play it 😍
This class & instructor fill me with positive vibes & chills! Love her energy!
Bf just came asking “why don’t you just ride why do you gotta listen to a video” cuz it helps I can’t push myself and it feels good to see and hear a woman motivating us to get fit and healthy
